name: Craig Warren
text: This is the best pizza.  We miss going to eat with our large family we would go for birthdays and other occasions. Just glad they are open and are still surviving they have the best customer service with everyone always smiles and happy.

name: Jewel K Kloth
text: Great meeting place for friends and family to reconnect.  Plus they have great wings! And my husband loves the Pizza!

name: Marisela Navarro
text: Love their pizzas. This is one of the best places to get pizza and pasta. They have a variety of options and they make exactly what you ask for. I recommend this place to anyone.

name: Dean Ariosa
text: I have yet to eat here but have been inside to buy Coca Cola cuz I work at the laundrynot at night.

name: Tim Reed
text: Very good food & service. Can't be beat

name: Dan Bokor
text:
Love their Pizza!!! Great service, Great Pizza!! Will keep going there.
Also THANKS for taking safety of your customers seriously!

name: William Galang
text: Great staff. Guillermo is the best. Been coming here for many years. At lest 25 years.

name: Jennie Galang
text: The pizza was horrible, we ordered two king size pizza's and there was giant burn air pockets on both with no sauce in the pizza. I've been going there for years and it was NEVER like that, the new people that got hired there is what's the problem now with bad customer service and pizza.

name: Padre Fernando Olivera Maga√±a
text: Good pizza, the place is clean but little bit dark

name: Sylvia Cortez
text: Love! Love! Love! Great atmosphere, delicious pizza and the staff is awesome!

name: Frank Perkins
text: We came in with a coupon for a large asked for a pan they didn't have one ready so gave us 2 mediums for the price of a soda.

name: Shuck N. Jive
text: Best pizza ever!  You got to come back to Torrance!!
